Instructions to make Timo's code run

conda create -p /lustre/projects/p001_swin/gvernardos/lsst_python_env/lsst_env python=2.7

source activate /lustre/projects/p001_swin/gvernardos/lsst_python_env/lsst_env
[There is a local cache in ~/anaconda/pkgs. You can also configure it to be anywhere you want by setting the envs_dirs option in your .condarc.]

conda config --add channels http://conda.lsst.codes/sims
conda install lsst-sims-maf
conda install astropy

TO UPDATE:

conda update lsst-sims-maf

TO RUN THE CODE DO:

source activate /lustre/projects/p001_swin/gvernardos/lsst_python_env/lsst_env

[for bash shell users] source eups-setups.sh 
[for (t)csh users] source [anaconda directory]/bin/eups-setups.csh 

setup sims_maf

python <script name>
